modules.description: Provides functions for parsing and manipulating binary data streams using bit-level operations and endianness conversion. Works with byte arrays, integers, and custom bit-packed structures. Enables efficient serialization and deserialization of network protocols and file formats.

Controls verbosity and result verification settings. Transforms and manipulates logical expressions in disjunctive normal form (DNF) using specified optimization algorithms, parses DNF expressions from strings or files, and generates string representations for debugging or output. Converts between string formats and internal boolean list structures for logical term representation.
